Harry Gribbon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Gribbon 0 Harry Gribbon (June 9, 1885 – July 28, 1961) was an American film actor. He appeared in 144 films between 1915 and 1938. He was the brother of actor Eddie Gribbon and worked for the obscure L-KO Kompany after starting out with Mack Sennett. Many of his films from this era have been lost.
